pageContext.claim: “All buildings now inspected........for safety. Thank you to the Governor of P.R. and to all of those who are working so closely with our First Responders. Fantastic job!”
pageContext.analysis: “I’m not aware of such inspection. Of course, there are areas of Puerto Rico which we haven’t really gotten in contact. Perhaps he was referring to a particular set of buildings. I’m not sure," said Puerto Rican Gov. Ricardo Rossello.
